  "response_content_data": "Great! I've set up a structured learning plan to help you learn how to play Minecraft. I've created a main objective: 'Learn to Play Minecraft', which is broken down into several sub-objectives, each with specific tasks to guide you.\n\nHere's an overview of your learning path:\n\n*   **Understand Basic Mechanics & Controls:** Starting with installing the game, creating your first world, and mastering movement and camera controls.\n*   **Resource Gathering & Crafting:** You'll learn to gather essential resources like wood and stone, and then craft basic tools and manage your hunger.\n*   **Building & Shelter:** This section focuses on constructing a basic survival shelter and crafting a bed to set your spawn point and skip the night.\n*   **Exploration & Combat:** Finally, you'll learn to identify different mobs, understand their behaviors, and practice basic combat techniques to survive in the game world.\n\nEach step has realistic due dates and actionable steps to help you progress. You'll also earn gamification points as you complete these objectives. Let me know when you're ready to start!",
  "action_summary_content": "Created a main objective 'Learn to Play Minecraft' (ID: 16ac0346-22f7-48de-bf52-a952e3c1cf60) with a due date of August 15, 2025. Under this, created the following sub-objectives and their associated tasks:\n\n1.  **Understand Basic Mechanics & Controls** (ID: 31d77a7c-442c-4763-bec0-d29847b282a8, Due: July 10, 2025)\n    *   Task: Install Minecraft & Create First World (ID: 5a77f8b7-64df-4675-b4aa-ef3f99c648ca, Due: July 6, 2025)\n    *   Task: Learn Movement & Camera Controls (ID: 6a23654f-0077-45e8-b0a0-30dd4baa1d1b, Due: July 7, 2025)\n\n2.  **Resource Gathering & Crafting** (ID: 13eadb3e-8f4d-4b6c-ae2a-71d14dd81b4b, Due: July 15, 2025)\n    *   Task: Gather Wood and Craft Wooden Tools (ID: 0b9099e1-2961-4941-b082-0061343d9e29, Due: July 10, 2025)\n    *   Task: Mine Stone and Craft Stone Tools (ID: 43ee65e9-8f85-4bea-8e66-881708d41e33, Due: July 12, 2025)\n    *   Task: Find Food & Manage Hunger (ID: e298341d-3593-4727-bb41-a5c939a65bef, Due: July 15, 2025)\n\n3.  **Building & Shelter** (ID: 62203fae-772c-4903-a6a3-c61eed475273, Due: July 25, 2025)\n    *   Task: Build a Basic Survival Shelter (ID: 3cb89e7f-50a9-4439-bde0-956dd55d2ce6, Due: July 18, 2025)\n    *   Task: Craft and Place a Bed (ID: 7dfa2f9c-c49e-4748-a79a-fabb094e1345, Due: July 20, 2025)\n\n4.  **Exploration & Combat** (ID: 7a60ce17-7326-4127-94f4-c1e177bdd089, Due: August 5, 2025)\n    *   Task: Identify Passive and Hostile Mobs (ID: fc0a840b-a289-4cda-bc68-b42a87dfcd6c, Due: July 28, 2025)\n    *   Task: Learn Basic Combat Techniques (ID: 7c894c39-87ad-4862-a7d0-f5fe874f5151, Due: August 2, 2025)\n\nAll objectives and tasks include descriptions, start/due dates, priority/complexity scores, energy requirements, context tags, success criteria, and points awarded for completion. Tasks also include estimated durations and actionable steps. The execution followed the planning agent's recommendations precisely, creating a comprehensive learning structure for the user's goal to learn Minecraft."
}
